You have defeated the Warg-matron of the Howling Wood, responsible for spawning and protecting the pack that settled so near Floodwend. With the matron defeated, the good Rohirrim of Floodwend are safer, and can hope to reclaim this abandoned worksite.
Wargs have recently moved into the work site to the east of Floodwend.
